 version 0.5:
 - Added HTML tree generation
 - Added "fields" support
 - Added charset support in curl module
 - Added HTML normalization through tree conversion
 - Added preliminary documentation
 - Added custom form-encoding method (without curl)
 - Updated split to support open tags without closing tags
 - Updated curl module to retry when error occurs
 - Updated form fields and actions handling
 - Updated attachments support
 - Changed attach file parameter to filename

